strings: <se_high>Jessica: Are you out of your mind!?
<se_def>Angelo: Why not!? Some of them need a bit of a nudge in the right direction.

<se_high>Jessica: Aren't you supposed to be a Templar?
I would have thought impersonating the Goddess is against the rules!
<se_def>Angelo: No problem there either! The Goddess I believe in doesn't care about nonsense like that!
<se_high>Jessica: Well, don't come crying to me if the Goddess drops a mountain on you or something!
